{"tid":2047131,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"做狗同投胎一樣，汪明荃3層西貢豪宅　海景景觀超開揚　唐狗被領養後過超豪生活","createTime":"2020-06-02T01:57:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T19:41:08.000Z","uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7312248f5abff167c8a1eb3809c046f86e1b1fa4","tid":2047131,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T01:57:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200515/338034358814380032.jpeg/VvaFg_dm7UfidfwvFuZWCDACoIQlmecFy6zsxMus7MQ?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200515%2F338034358814380032.jpeg%2FVvaFg_dm7UfidfwvFuZWCDACoIQlmecFy6zsxMus7MQ%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=3c35b600&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n汪明荃在娛樂圈立足多年，早已建立起江湖地位。不過回到家中，她卻是一位溫柔的狗主，早已把家中兩隻唐狗當成自己子女。現在深居簡出享受生活，與丈夫羅家英及兩隻唐狗，生活在西貢3層高世外桃源豪宅裏。"},{"pid":"6f336e1e6db0b30c7a6cd05a8c95a02307df9747","tid":2047131,"uid":40272,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T03:06:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/veKkbLa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FveKkbLa.jpg&h=973ea39f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89956bc4d5f1693d749ee760b5db7364e674e753","tid":2047131,"uid":24160,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T19:32:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/cAg0Day.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FcAg0Day.gif&h=7884fa01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36863bb66c7094526b5190386608d19174467650","tid":2047131,"uid":193642,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T19:41:08.000Z","msg":"無仔女，啲錢用曬用養寵物"}]}